oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Banner of the Association of Confederate Soldiers of Murfreesboro, Tennessee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Banner of the Association of Confederate Soldiers - Tennessee Department. Banner is red with gold lettering reading, "Joe B. Palmer Bivouac A. C. S. T. D. No. 10. Mufreesboro, Tenn." with an image of Joe B. Palmer in the middle framed by laurel leaves.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Metro Archives, Nashville, Davidson County, Tennessee
